IRC Bot
zum Loggen des Chat-Verlaufs.

Plugins
müssen die Interfaces createTable(database), addEntry(database, order, who, message) und lastSeen(database, person) implementieren und im Unterordner _plugins_ abgelegt werden.

usage: simplebot.py [-h] [-s HOST] [-p PORT] [-n NICK] [-i IDENT]
                    [-r REAL_NAME] [-c CHANNEL] [--pass PASSWORD] [-D]
                    [-d DEAMON_STOP] [--mhost MAIL_HOST]
                    [--maddress MAIL_ADDRESS] [--musername MAIL_USERNAME]
                    [--mpass MAIL_PASSWORD] [--msubject MAIL_SUBJECT]
                    [--plugin PLUGIN] [--plugin-location PLUGIN_LOCATION]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s HOST               IRC server
  -p PORT               IRC port
  -n NICK               IRC nick
  -i IDENT              IRC ident
  -r REAL_NAME          IRC real name
  -c CHANNEL            IRC channel
  --pass PASSWORD       IRC password for closing the bot
  -D                    Deactivate deamon behaviour
  -d DEAMON_STOP        Stopping (-d stop) or restarting (-d restart) daemon
  --mhost MAIL_HOST     eMail host
  --maddress MAIL_ADDRESS
                        eMail address
  --musername MAIL_USERNAME
                        eMail username
  --mpass MAIL_PASSWORD
                        eMail password
  --msubject MAIL_SUBJECT
                        eMail subject
  --plugin PLUGIN       logging plugin
  --plugin-location PLUGIN_LOCATION
                        absolute location of logs